title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Disruptions to routine could upset some of the creatures of habit in your daily social circle, at work or home today. But truth be told, you enjoy the excitement of an occasional surprise. Instead of being unnerved when puzzle pieces are thrown into the air, you are curious about the picture they will form when they land. Your naturally quick responses and mental agility are empowering and inspiring. When change is afoot, you are in one of your favorite wheelhouses. Navigate with confidence and show others how its done. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
